dataIdInfo.idAbs: This polygon data layer represents zoning for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2010. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Calumet_Zoning_2010.gdb.[This is a polygon shapefile/geodatabase feature class that depicts the county zoning information.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[The zoning data was created to assist the county Planning and Zoning Department in their decision making and to keep accruate and current geographic data.]
